# Environment Variables for Production

## Backend (Server) - Required for deployment
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://username:password@host:port/insta_game
REDIS_URL=redis://host:port
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here
PORT=3000
ADMIN_SECRET=your-admin-secret-key

## Frontend (Client) - Optional
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.com
# VITE_ADSENSE_CLIENT=ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

## Instructions:
# 1. For backend deployment (Railway, Render, etc.):
#    - Add all DATABASE_URL, REDIS_URL, JWT_SECRET to your hosting platform
#    - Generate a strong JWT_SECRET using: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
#
# 2. For frontend deployment (Netlify):
#    - If backend is on different domain, add VITE_API_URL
#    - After AdSense approval, add VITE_ADSENSE_CLIENT
#
# 3. Database Setup:
#    - You can use:
#      * Neon (https://neon.tech) - Free serverless Postgres
#      * Supabase (https://supabase.com) - Free tier with Postgres
#      * Railway (https://railway.app) - Free tier
#
# 4. Redis Setup:
#    - You can use:
#      * Upstash (https://upstash.com) - Free serverless Redis
#      * Redis Cloud (https://redis.com) - Free tier
#      * Railway (https://railway.app) - Includes Redis
